snippet.title: Last Labyrinth Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Last Labyrinth is a VR Escape-the-Room Adventure that pairs you with a mysterious girl as you try to escape a mansion filled with hidden dangers.

For more information, visit the official Last Labyrinth website: https://lastlabyrinth.jp/en
